{"word":"G641 - ἀποῤῥίπτω - aporrhíptō - ap-or-hrip'-to - Cast","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποῤῥίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aporrhíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-or-hrip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cast</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழு"},{"paragraph":"to throw away, cast down; reflexively, to cast oneself down"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G4496 - ῥίπτω - rhíptō - hrip'-to/4496\">G4496</a>; to <i>hurl off</i>, that is, <i>precipitate</i> (oneself): - cast.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1977/1977\">G1977</a>, <a href=\"#/G4495/4495\">G4495</a>, <a href=\"#/G4496/4496\">G4496</a>, <a href=\"#/G641/641\">G641</a>"}]}